msgid ""
"**MAG (Mathematics and Graphics)** is a modern-cpp math library built for"
" use in 3D graphics. The library targets **C++20 and newer**, uses **C++ "
"modules**, and ships a compact API for vector math, matrix math, "
"transform helpers, constants, and optional SIMD acceleration."
